assets.description:
So Rave is my Sonic OC (has been for about 6 years now) and one of his defining features is a orange-flame emblazoned robotic arm. He's gone through several revisions but I think the current design is definitely the best (created by my friend Sharlet). this design features a zero-gravity hand, suspended in the air with separated digits. This is a (very) low poly model depicting it's basic features. ^^

I'm not quite done with it yet, but I like what it looks like so far. ^^
